@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_luqtlh(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = tmp
    v2 = wp.abs((v1 / wp.abs(tmp + 0.06)))
    v2 = wp.abs((wp.exp(v2 + 0.05) - (v2 + 0.30 / tmp + 0.74)))
    v1 = v0
    data[tid] = v0
